overview: Yui who thought that happiness would continue forever ... However, one day she is raped by a group of four men. Yui transforms from hatred to a woman with all white eyes of revenge. She turned into a demon of revenge, and she took out the spirit of the rapers and preyed on them one by one. A woman with white eyes caught by them inserts a thick decachin into her delicate body.
title: Zombie-Eyed Nympho 3 Yui Otokawa
